                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="3"><strong>Dear Sir/Madam,</strong></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td valign="top" width="15%" style="text-align:right;padding-top:15px"><strong>Reference:</strong></td>
                                <td colspan="2" width="85%" style="padding-left:20px;padding-top:15px;text-align: justify;">Intimation and consent regarding modification of sanctioned plans with respect to the Project <strong>“MAHENDRA ARTO – HELIX”</strong> situated at Sinus. 275/1 &amp; 275/2, Hulimangala Village, Jigani Hobli, Anekal Taluk, Bengaluru Urban.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td valign="top" width="15%" style="text-align:right;padding-top:15px"><strong>Subject:</strong></td>
                                <td colspan="2" style="padding-left:20px;padding-top:15px;text-align: justify;">Agreement for Sale dated <apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!Booking__c.Sale_Agreement_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText> with respect to the Apartment No. {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Name}, {!FloorNumber} of {!Booking__c.Block__r.Name} in the Project <strong>“MAHENDRA ARTO – HELIX”</strong>.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="3" style="padding-top:15px;text-align: justify;" >This is with respect to, obtaining consent from you for the proposed modification of sanctioned plans of the above project. In this regard, please note the following:</td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                        
                        <ol >
                            <li><p style="text-align: justify;">With reference to the above Project  “MAHENDRA ARTO – HELIX”  being developed by us which has been registered with the Karnataka Real Estate Regulatory Authority under the Real Estate ( Regulation and Development ) Act, 2016 (ACT) and Karnataka Real Estate (Regulation and Development )Rules, 2017 (RULES) on 27.07.2023 vide registration No. PRM/KA/RERA/1251/308/PR/270723/006099</p></li>
                            <li><p style="text-align: justify;">In view of the provisions of the Act and Rules applicable to the project and in view of the proposed modification, the sanctioned building plan of the Project will be changed by virtue of the modified sanction plan, the building in the Project may include additional floors and increase in number of units in each Tower which will be informed after obtaining the modified plan sanction. Apart from the said modifications, there are no other changes proposed to the sanctioned building plan. </p></li>
                            <li><p style="text-align: justify;">The Plan has been sanctioned by the Bangalore Development Authority (BDA) vide No. ಬೆಂಅಪ್ರಾ/ನಮ/ಅಸ/ಅಅ-3/ತಾಸ-2/ದ/46/2022-23, dated 27.03.2023 for construction of Multistoried Residential Apartment Complex consisting of 273 units in 2 Towers (i.e. Tower-A comprising of 134 Units consisting of 2BF+GF+24 Upper Floors and, Tower-B comprising of 139 Units consisting of with 2BF+GF+23 Upper Floors) and Amenity Block comprising of Ground and First Floors.</p></li>
                            <li><p style="text-align: justify;">The application to modify the Plan sanction will be applied with the jurisdictional Planning/Sanctioning authority being the BDA, after completion of due process and obtaining NOC from the Authority.</p></li>
                            
                        </ol>
                    </div>
