                          <li style="list-style: none;"></li>
                           <li style="list-style: none;"></li>
                            <li><p style="text-align: justify;">It is hereby informed to you that as per the modified building plan, the Apartment proposed to be purchased by you may undergo the following changes.</p></li>
                        </ol>
