                           <li style="list-style: none;"></li>
                            <li style="list-style: none;"></li>
                            <li>As a result of the modification, the time for completion of the Project will not be changed. We will take necessary steps for completion of the modified plan as per the provisions of the Act and will fulfill our contractual obligations in respect of your Apartment.</li>
                            <li>We request your co-operation in this regard. We request you to sign a copy of this letter and send it back to us, acknowledging the information being given to you regarding the proposed modification of the sanctioned building plan for the Project and giving your consent for the same, which shall be treated as consent under Section 14(2) (ii) of the Act, to enable us to do the needful. </li>
                        </ol>
                        
                        <p>Thanking You</p>
